h1. Redmine Bootstrap

Redmine Bootstrap is a an attempt to make a simple there for Redmine. This is very much a work in progress. This has been developed on Redmine version 0.9.

Collaborators welcome!

h2. Installation

Pull this directory out into your /redmine/public/themes/ folder.

In Redmine, under Administration find Settings. Depending on the Redmine version, there will either be a Display tab, or a single configuration page with a Theme dropdown. Select the new theme and save.
